OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and wet start to the
OL,6,Fday, with rain gradually clearing
OL,7,Fthrough the morning. Turning brighter,
OL,8,Fwith plenty of sunny spells developing
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon. Perhaps an
OL,10,Fisolated shower remains possible.
OL,11,FFeeling warmer than of late, but
OL,12,Frather breezy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FPlenty of late sunny spells
OL,15,Fduring the evening and staying largely
OL,16,Fdry. Prolonged clear spells overnight,
OL,17,Fwith winds falling light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
