OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA dry day, with lighter
OL,6,Fwinds. Feeling pleasant in the
OL,7,Fdeveloping sunshine, though this
OL,8,Fturning hazy at times, mainly in the
OL,9,Fnorth.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA fine
OL,12,Ffew days on Sunday and Monday, with
OL,13,Fplenty of warm spells of sunshine and
OL,14,Flight winds. Perhaps an increasing
OL,15,Frisk of showers developing later on
OL,16,FTuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
